# Code Organization Rules

## File Structure
- Styles should be always tailwind CSS or in last case `src/styles`

## Naming Conventions
- Use PascalCase for component names (e.g., `PlayerComponent.jsx`)
- Use camelCase for functions and variables
- Use UPPER_SNAKE_CASE for constants

## Code Style
- Keep components small and focused
- Use always tailwind CSS

## Git Rules
- Write meaningful commit messages
- Keep commits focused and atomic
- Follow conventional commits format

## Performance Rules
- Lazy load components when possible
- Optimize images and assets
- Use proper memoization techniques

## Documentation
- only important comments